# FMCG Promotion Impact Forecasting System

An end-to-end AI-powered retail intelligence platform that forecasts product sales, predicts promotion uplift, and simulates promotion ROI for FMCG stores — built on the Rossmann Store Sales dataset.

---

## Project Summary

Retailers spend millions on promotions without knowing the exact impact in advance. This system uses machine learning to forecast sales, measure promotion uplift, and recommend whether a promotion is worth running — before any budget is committed.

---

## Results

| Metric | Score |
|--------|-------|
| Model | XGBoost |
| Training Records | 813,118 |
| Features Engineered | 39 |
| Model MAPE | 9.85% |
| Baseline MAPE | 18.55% |
| Improvement | 47% better than baseline |
| Avg Promotion Uplift | 38.8% |

---

## System Architecture

```
[ DATA LAYER ]
Raw Rossmann CSVs → Preprocessing Pipeline → Feature Engineering

[ ML LAYER ]
Baseline Model → XGBoost Forecaster → Uplift Model → SHAP Explainer

[ API LAYER ]
FastAPI → /predict-sales → /predict-uplift → /simulate-promotion

[ DASHBOARD LAYER ]
Streamlit → Overview → Simulator → SHAP Page → Store Analytics
```

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|------------|
| Language | Python 3.14 |
| ML Model | XGBoost |
| Explainability | SHAP |
| Backend API | FastAPI |
| Dashboard | Streamlit |
| Visualization | Plotly |
| Data Processing | Pandas, NumPy |
| Deployment | Docker |

